# Configurations

auto-reload yes
reload-threads 3
download-timeout 120
feed-sort-order lastupdated
cleanup-on-quit yes

## A browser setting that works on both Debian and MacOS
browser "command -v chromium 1>/dev/null && chromium -incognito %u || /Applications/Firefox.app/Contents/MacOS/firefox --private-window %u"


# Key bindings

bind o everywhere open-in-browser-and-mark-read
bind <S-o> everywhere open-all-unread-in-browser

## Vi like key bindings
bind k everywhere up
bind j everywhere down
bind <C-f> everywhere pagedown
bind <C-d> everywhere halfpagedown
bind <C-b> everywhere pageup
bind <C-u> everywhere halfpageup

